    "XXbsu004_u:284": " sarvadoṣebhyaḥ phaṭ /",
    "XXbsu004_u:285": " om ṣṭrau bandha 2 duṣṭān rakṣa 2 māṃ sarvasattvānāṃ svāhā /",
    "XXbsu004_u:286": " ye kecin mama sarvasattvānāṃ ca duṣṭā duṣṭacittā raudrā raudracittā pāpāḥ pāpacittāḥ kupitāḥ kupitacittā amitrā amitracittā /",
    "XXbsu004_u:287": " ete mama sarvasattvānāṃ ca rakṣāṃ kurvantu jīvantu varṣaśataṃ paśyantu śaradāṃ śatam /",
    "XXbsu004_u:288": " ye kecidyakṣagrahāḥ, vratāhārāḥ,",
    "XXbsu004_u:289": " garbhāhārāḥ, rudhirāhārāḥ, baṃśāhārāḥ {vasāhārāḥ}, māṃsāhāraḥ, medāhārāḥ,",
    "XXbsu004_u:290": " majjāhārāḥ, jātāhārāḥ, jīvitāhārāḥ, valyāhārāḥ, mālyāhārāḥ, gandhāhārāḥ,",
    "XXbsu004_u:291": " puṣpāhārāḥ, dhūpāhārāḥ, phalāhārāḥ, āhutyāhārāḥ, vittāhārāḥ, cittāhārāḥ,",
    "XXbsu004_u:292": " pūjāhārāḥ, mudrāhārāḥ, śleṣmāhārāḥ, kheṭāhārāḥ, siṃghāṇakāhārāḥ,",
    "XXbsu004_u:293": " vātāhārāḥ, viriktāhārāḥ, aśucyāhārāḥ, spandanikāhārāḥ /",
    "XXbsu004_u:294": " pāpacittāḥ,",
    "XXbsu004_u:295": " duṣṭacittāḥ, raudracittāḥ, devagrahāḥ, nāgagrahāḥ, yakṣagrahāḥ,",
    "XXbsu004_u:296": " rākṣasagrahāḥ, gandharvagrahāḥ, asuragrahāḥ, garuḍagrahāḥ, kinnaragrahāḥ,",
    "XXbsu004_u:297": " mahoragagrahāḥ, manuṣyagrahāḥ, amanuṣyagrahāḥ, marutagrahāḥ, piśācagrahāḥ,",
    "XXbsu004_u:298": " bhūtagrahāḥ, kumbhāṇḍagrahāḥ, pūtanagrahāḥ, kaṭapūtanagrahāḥ,",
    "XXbsu004_u:299": " skandagrahāḥ, unmādagrahāḥ, chāyāgrahāḥ, apasmāragrahāḥ, ostāḍakagrahāḥ,",
    "XXbsu004_u:300": " ḍākinīgrahāḥ, revatīgrahāḥ, śamikāgrahāḥ, jāmakagrahāḥ {yāmakagrahāḥ},",
    "XXbsu004_u:301": " śakunigrahāḥ, mātṛnandigrahāḥ, kambukāminīgrahāḥ, alambanagrahāḥ,",
    "XXbsu004_u:302": " kaṭaḍākinīgrahāḥ, kaṃṭakamālinīgrahāḥ, sarvagrahāḥ /",
    "XXbsu004_u:303": " jvarā ekāhikāḥ, dvaitīyakāḥ, traitīyakāḥ, cāturthikāḥ, saptāhikāḥ,",
    "XXbsu004_u:304": " arddhamāsikāḥ, māsikāḥ, dvaimāsikāḥ, mauhūrttikāḥ, nityajvarāḥ,",
    "XXbsu004_u:305": " viṣamajvarāḥ, (Sitā 153) pretajvarāḥ, piśācajvarāḥ, mānuṣajvarāḥ,",
    "XXbsu004_u:306": " amānuṣajvarāḥ, vātikāḥ, paittikāḥ, ślaiṣmikāḥ, sānnipātikāḥ, sarvajvarāḥ śirovartimapanayantu mama sarvasattvānāṃ ca arddhāvabhedakam, arocakam akṣirogaṃ nāsarogaṃ mukharogaṃ kaṇṭharogaṃ hṛdrogaṃ galagrahaṃ karṇaśūlaṃ dantaśūlam uraḥśūlaṃ hṛdayaśūlaṃ marmaśūlaṃ pṛṣṭhaśūlam udaraśūlaṃ",
    "XXbsu004_u:307": " vastiśūlaṃ gudaśūlaṃ yoniśūlaṃ pradaraśūlam ūrūśūlaṃ jaṅghāśūlaṃ hastaśūlaṃ pādaśūlam aṅgapratyaṅgaśūlaṃ mama cāpanayantu /",
    "XXbsu004_u:308": " bhūtapretavetālaḍākinījvaradagdhakaṇḍūkiṭībhakuṣṭapittakaplīhabhagaṃdaralūtāpāmāvaisarpalohaliṅgāśeṣaśvāsatrāsakāsamūrchāgaraviṣayayogāgnyudakamāramārīkalahavairakāntārākālamṛtyutryambukatrailāṭakavṛścikasarpanakulasiṃhavyāghrarkṣatarakṣucarmaramakaravṛkataskarājīvakāyikānapanayantu",
    "XXbsu004_u:309": " {Śambuka(tai)lāṭaŚ}/ anyeṣāṃ sarveṣāṃ sitātapatramahoṣṇīṣamahāpratyaṅgirāvidyānubhāvena yāvad dvādaśayojanābhyantareṇa pañcāśatayojanābhyantareṇa vā vidyābandhaṃ karomi tejobandhanaṃ karomi sarvavidyābandhanaṃ karomi paravidyābandhanaṃ karomi",
    "XXbsu004_u:310": " sīmābandhanaṃ karomi dharaṇībandhanaṃ karomi daśadigbandhanaṃ karomi parasainyastambhanaṃ karomi /",
    "XXbsu004_u:311": " tadyathā om anane 2 khakhane 2 vīṣama 2 vīre",
    "XXbsu004_u:312": " 2 maunya 2 śānte 2 dānte 2 vajradhara bandhabandhani vajrapāṇe phaṭ /",
    "XXbsu004_u:313": " om hūṃ ṣṭroṃ phaṭ 2 svāhā /",
    "XXbsu004_u:314": " om vajrapāśe bandha 2 vajrapāśaṃ ca sarvaduṣṭavighnavināyakān hūṃ phaṭ 2 rakṣa 2 māṃ sarvasattvāṃśca svāhā /",
    "XXbsu004_u:315": " ya imāṃ sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatrānāmāparājitāpratyaṅgirāmahāvidyārājñīṃ likhitvā bhūrjapatre vastre vā valkale vā kāyagataṃ vā kaṇṭhagataṃ vā kṛtvā dhārayiṣyati vāciṣyati aśuddhakaṃ na kṣamiṣyati /",
    "XXbsu004_u:316": " sarvakṛtyakarma na kramiṣyati /",
    "XXbsu004_u:317": " nagaraṃ kramiṣyati, yogaṃ kramiṣyati, nākālamṛtyunā kālaṃ kariṣyati /",
    "XXbsu004_u:318": " sarvagrahāṇāṃ sarvavighnavināyakānāṃ ca priyo bhaviṣyati /",
    "XXbsu004_u:319": " manaāpaścaturaśītikalpakoṭīsahasrāṇi jātau jātau jātismaro bhaviṣyati caturaśītivajrakulakoṭiniyutaśatasahasrāṇi vidyādevatā nityaṃ satatasamitaṃ tasya rakṣāvaraṇaguptiṃ kariṣyanti /",
    "XXbsu004_u:320": " caturaśītivajradūtī kiṃkarā nityaṃ paripālayiṣyanti teṣāmapi priyo bhaviṣyati /",
    "XXbsu004_u:321": " manaāpaśca na kadācidyakṣatvaṃ na rākṣasatvaṃ na bhūtatvaṃ na piśācatvaṃ na pūtanatvaṃ na kaṭapūtanatvaṃ na manuṣyadāridryaṃ pratyanubhaviṣyati /",
    "XXbsu004_u:322": " gaṅgānadībālukāsaṃkhyeyāprameyāṇāṃ buddhānāṃ bhagavatāṃ puṇyaskandhena samanvāgato bhaviṣyati",
    "XXbsu004_u:323": " imāṃ ca sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatrānāmāparājitāṃ pratyaṅgirāṃ mahavidyārājñīṃ dhārayamāṇa abrahmacārī brahmacārī bhaviṣyati /",
    "XXbsu004_u:324": " amaunī maunī bhaviṣyati /",
    "XXbsu004_u:325": " aśuciḥ śucirbhaviṣyati /",
    "XXbsu004_u:326": " anupavāsī upavāsī bhaviṣyati /",
    "XXbsu004_u:327": " yo 'pi",
    "XXbsu004_u:328": " pañcānantaryakārī syāt so 'pi (Sitā 154) nirdhūtapāpo bhaviṣyati /",
    "XXbsu004_u:329": " pūrvakarmāvaraṇaṃ niravaśeṣaṃ parikṣayaṃ gacchati /",
    "XXbsu004_u:330": " yaḥ kaścit mātṛgrāme tathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatrānāmāparājitā mahāpratyaṅgirā mahāvidyārājñīṃ dhārayamāṇaḥ putrārthī putraṃ pratilabhate /",
    "XXbsu004_u:331": " āyuḥpuṇyabalaṃ pratilabhate /",
    "XXbsu004_u:332": " itaścyutvā sukhavatyāṃ lokadhātāvupapadyate /",
    "XXbsu004_u:333": " sa ca rāgadveṣamohamānadarpavigato bhaviṣyati /",
    "XXbsu004_u:334": " yaḥ kaścinmanuṣyamāre paśumāre gomāre sarve 'pyupadravopasargopāyāsaparacakrāgamaneṣu tasya bhagavato jinasya samyaksaṃbuddhasya sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatrānāmāparājitāṃ",
    "XXbsu004_u:335": " dhvajāgrāvaropitāṃ kṛtvā mahatā pūjāsatkāreṇa mahatīṃ pūjāṃ kṛtvā sarvanagaradvāreṣu praveśayet vihāre vā grāme vā nagare vā janapade vā nigame vā śmaśāne vā parvate vā araṇyāyatane vā imāmaparājitāṃ pratyaṅgirāṃ vidyārājñīṃ mahatā satkāreṇa praveśayet /",
    "XXbsu004_u:336": " praveśitamātreṇa praśāntikṛto bhaviṣyati /",
    "XXbsu004_u:337": " sarve 'pyupadravopasargopāyāsāḥ paracakrāṇi praśāmyanti /",
    "XXbsu004_u:338": " ananto nāgarājā śaṅkhapālo nāgarājā mahākṛṣṇo nāgarājā nandyupanaṃdau nāgarājānau anye ca sarve te nāgarājānaḥ kāle ca kālaṃ varṣayiṣyanti kālena kālaṃ autsukyamāpatsyate /",
    "XXbsu004_u:339": " kālena kālaṃ garjayiṣyanti sarvarogopadravāṃścopaśamayiṣyanti /",
    "XXbsu004_u:340": " om ṣṭroṃ bandha 2 sarvaduṣṭān rakṣa 2",
    "XXbsu004_u:341": " māṃ sarvasattvāṃśca svāhā /",
    "XXbsu004_u:342": " om hūṃ ṣṭroṃ bandha 2 duṣṭān rakṣa 2 māṃ sarvasattvāṃśca vajrapāṇe hūṃ phaṭ svāhā /",
    "XXbsu004_u:343": " om sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣa avalokitamūrdhni tejorāśi /",
    "XXbsu004_u:344": " om jvala 2 dhak 2 khāda 2 dara 2 vidara 2",
    "XXbsu004_u:345": " chinte {chinda} 2 bhinda 2 hūṃ 2 phaṭ 3 rakṣa 2 māṃ sarvasattvāṃśca svāhā",
    "XXbsu004_u:346": " / om sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatre hūṃ phaṭ /",
    "XXbsu004_u:347": " om rakṣa 2 māṃ sarvasattvāṃśca hūṃ phaṭ svāhā /",
    "XXbsu004_u:348": " tadyathā - om anale 2 acare 2 khasame 2",
    "XXbsu004_u:349": " vīre 2 saumye 2 sarvabuddhādhiṣṭhānādhiṣṭhite sarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatre sarvaduṣṭacittān hūṃ phaṭ svāhā /",
    "XXbsu004_u:350": " buddhayogena sarvopadraveṣu trijaptā kartavyā /",
    "XXbsu004_u:351": " sarvabuddhabodhisattvāśca sadevamānuṣāsuragaruḍakinnaramahoragaśca loko bhagavato bhāṣitamabhyanandanniti",
    "XXbsu004_u:352": " āryasarvatathāgatoṣṇīṣasitātapatrānāmaparājitā pratyaṅgirā mahāvidyārājñī samāptā //"
}